Enterprise License
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

The Enterprise License ($199/year per organisation) grants the following
additional rights on top of the MIT License:

  1. Priority support with 24-hour response SLA
  2. Access to the Admin Dashboard for API monitoring and analytics
  3. Advanced caching features (distributed cache adapters)
  4. Multi-tenancy utilities and tenant-scoped query helpers
  5. Detailed performance reports and query profiling
  6. Priority inclusion of feature requests in the roadmap
  7. Early access to new releases and pre-release builds

To purchase an Enterprise License, contact: enterprise@gofastapi.dev
or visit: https://gofastapi.dev/enterprise

Organizations with fewer than 5 developers or revenue below USD 100,000/year
may use all features under the MIT License at no cost.
